column4: Hackers Hit US Congressional Web Sites; Insult President Obama
The cyber attack occurred just hours after Mr. Obama finished delivering his State of the Union address in Washington
According to messages left by hackers on some sites, a group calling itself the "Red Eye Crew" claimed responsibility for the infiltration, which left messages saying, in part, "F--- Obama."
